               ana="#taxonomy.3.7.2.3 #topic.324">Je kdo proti?</u>
            <note xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.26" type="vote">1 poslanec.</note>
            <u xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.27"
               who="#BizjakIvan1956"
               ana="#taxonomy.3.7.2.3 #topic.324">Se je kdo vzdržal?</u>
            <note xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.28" type="vote">7 poslancev.</note>
            <u xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.29"
               who="#BizjakIvan1956"
               ana="#taxonomy.3.7.2.3 #topic.324">Ugotavljam, da je z večino glasov ta amandma sprejet.</u>
            <u xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.30"
               who="#BizjakIvan1956"
               ana="#taxonomy.3.7.2.3 #topic.324">Preden gremo na glasovanje o predlogih sklepov, dajem na glasovanje predlog zakona v celoti, skupaj s sprejetimi amandmaji.</u>
            <u xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.31"
               who="#BizjakIvan1956"
               ana="#taxonomy.3.7.2.3 #topic.324">Kdo je za?</u>
            <note xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.32" type="vote">40 poslancev.</note>
            <u xml:id="ZbObc.1992-07-23.s040-04.sp-508.33"
